      * IN022-SLS-BSE-BEG-DTE: IF THE STORE HAS AN ACTUAL BOOKED                
      *      INVENTORY PRIOR TO THE OPEN MONTH, THIS IS THE INVENTORY           
      *      DATE + 1 DAY. IF NOT, THIS IS THE STORE OPEN DATE.                 
      * IN022-SLS-BSE-END-DTE: IF THE STORE HAS AN ACTUAL INVENTORY             
      *      (BOOKED OR UNBOOKED) IN THE OPEN MONTH, THIS IS THE                
      *      INVENTORY DATE. IF NOT, THIS IS BLANK.                             
      * IN022-UNBKD-INV-IND: IF THE STORE HAS AN ACTUAL UNBOOKED                
      *      INVENTORY IN THE OPEN MONTH, THIS INDICATOR IS SET TO 'Y'.         
      *      IF NOT, IT IS SET TO 'N'.                                          
